cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.IR, cs.SI

The paper focuses on the impact of new technologies on supply chains and the related cyber risks, which falls under the domain of cybersecurity (cs.CR) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the integration of supply chains in new technologies, which can be related to software engineering (cs.SE) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper presents an analytical framework for the mitigation of cyber risks, which can be related to systems and control (cs.SI).
